Great opportunity for first time home buyers, and investors!! 

This is a classic rambler, with 2 bedrooms and 1 bath on the main level. The unfinished basement provides future equity potential. 

Fenced in back yard with an oversized 2.5 stall garage to add your workshop, or provide extra storage for personal items.
